description:
Valve released today Proton 9.0 as the latest stable release of this open-source compatibility tool for Steam Play based on Wine and additional components that lets you play Windows games on Linux systems.

The post Proton 9.0 Released with Support for THE FINALS, Lord of the Rings: Gollum appeared first on Linux Today.
title: Proton 9.0 Released with Support for THE FINALS, Lord of the Rings: Gollum

description:
RHEL 9.4 is here, updated with Python 3.12, PHP 8.2, Podman 4.9, new identity management features, enhanced security, and more.

The post Red Hat Enterprise Linux 9.4 Released, Here’s What’s New appeared first on Linux Today.
title: Red Hat Enterprise Linux 9.4 Released, Here’s What’s New
